
----ADMIN CONSOLE----
(Step One) Within the "Travel Reimbursement" scope, search the application and select the Module of Submissions for Tasks/Incidents.

(Step Two) Right-click in the column header and select Configure>Workflows.

(Step Three) Click "New."

(Step Four) Input the values for "Name" and "Description."

(Step Five) Click "Submit."

-----WORKFLOW EDITOR-----
(Step Six) Go back to the Workflow Editor and add the following items from the Core Panel (See Workflow Example.JPG):
  -Approval User
  -Create Task
  -Set Values (Approved)
  -Set Values (Rejected)
 
 (Step Seven) Go to the Workflow Actions tab and select "Validate Workflow."
 
 (Step Eight) Publish it.
